snippet.title: Project Grove Prologue | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Alchemists!
Ready yourselves, from 11th September 2021 you will be able to play the FREE Project Grove Prologue on Steam.

✨ Play our Prologue✨ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1629470/Project_Grove_Prologue/ 

Enjoy your free sneak peek of Project Grove & let us know what you think below! 

Talk to us! ➡️ https://discord.gg/UTE3YJn
Follow our rambles! ➡️ https://twitter.com/Antler_Studios
Wishlist the Full Game  ➡️ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1175600/Project_Grove/
